cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper discusses curriculum learning in the context of deep neural networks, specifically in the areas of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper provides theoretical analysis and empirical experiments on the effectiveness of curriculum learning in these areas, making it relevant to multiple sub-categories.
